  <?dbhtml filename="glproto.html"?>

  <title>glproto-&glproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This extension defines a protocol for the client to send 3D rendering
      commands to the X server.
    </para>

